        <abstract> 
<p>Asks whether he can start soon on translating <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Thinks CD has gone a little too far on St G. J. Mivart’s objection, which he thinks did very little harm in Germany.</p> 
<p>JVC’s history of zoology is finished [<hi rend="italic">Geschichte der Zoologie bis auf Joh. Müller und Charl. Darwin</hi> (1872)].</p> 
